room_title: Escape room "The Wizard's Chamber" by Escape Room Cleveland in Cleveland
review: We had a great time. The wizard room was difficult but so fun. Amazing and elaborate --full of surprises! I won't spoil anything but think fast and trust your instincts. We will definitely be back. Loved it.

room_title: Escape room "The Wizard's Chamber" by Escape Room Cleveland in Cleveland
review: We booked the Wizard escape room for my daughters 13th birthday party. Her and 6 friends had an absolute blast. Staff was AMAZING! Definitely worth the 2 hr drive from Toledo. Wish we lived closer!!!

room_title: Escape room "The Wizard's Chamber" by Escape Room Cleveland in Cleveland
review: This is a great escape room. Had a blast in the Wizards Chamber with my group and were able to just get out in the nick of time. The other rooms look fun and i can't wait to try them!
